title: Bug 121687: Exception thrown when exporting data in table inside a grid cell
OB: When exporting data in a table that is inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown. Specifically, the exception occurs in the 'ReportEngineService.getMetaData()' function.
EB: When exporting data in two tables, the expected result is that the data is successfully exported without any exceptions.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Insert a grid.
2. Export data in two tables.
